metadata.title: RMIS: Catch & Effort Database 4.0
metadata.description: The Catch & Effort Database is an on-line database that houses catch & Effort and Location data.  Using the Query System 4.0 application, the user is allow to build a query by catch & effort and location codes.  The user is then allowed to optionally preview the result set row by row, and run a RMIS formatted report of their chose using the result set.  The report may then be returned to the browser, or sent to a user-entered email address.  Review the
